metaText.title: 2r. Beatus vir
metaText.history: transcribed from the Musica Alamire facsimile of the original printed in Antwerp by Petrum Phalesium, 1609
unalignedWords: Blessed is the man that shall continue in wisdom,
And that shall meditate in his justice,
And in his mind shall think of the all seeing eye of God.
